OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fwill clear this evening. The rest of
OL,7,Fthe night will be dry with clear
OL,8,Fspells, allowing some patches of mist
OL,9,Fand fog to develop.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FAny early morning mist or fog
OL,12,Fpatches quickly clearing. Then dry and
OL,13,Fsettled for the rest of the day with a
OL,14,Fgood deal of sunshine. Warm in the
OL,15,Fwest.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,18,Fand settled throughout this period
OL,19,Fwith a good deal of sunshine. Light
OL,20,Fwinds at first but becoming breezier
OL,21,Fby Thursday on eastern coasts.
